@baseurl=http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/collabsphere

### Send Mail - Single Recipient
POST {{baseurl}}/sendMail
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "data": {
        "to": ["sarankumarsk115@gmail.com"],
        "subject": "Welcome to CollabSphere",
        "body": "<h1>Welcome!</h1><p>You have been successfully onboarded to CollabSphere.</p>"
    }
}

###

### Send Mail - Multiple Recipients with CC and BCC
POST {{baseurl}}/sendMail
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "data": {
        "to": ["sarankumarsk115@gmail.com"],
        "cc": ["sarankumarsk115@gmail.com"],
        "bcc": ["sarankumarsk115@gmail.com"],
        "subject": "Project Kickoff - CollabSphere",
        "body": "<h2>Project Kickoff</h2><p>Dear Team,</p><p>This is to inform you that the project has officially kicked off. Please review the details and reach out if you have any questions.</p><br/><p>Regards,<br/>CollabSphere Team</p>"
    }
}

###

### Send Mail - With Attachment
POST {{baseurl}}/sendMail
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "data": {
        "to": ["sarankumarsk115@gmail.com"],
        "cc": ["sarankumarsk115@gmail.com"],
        "subject": "Employee Onboarding Documents",
        "body": "<p>Please find the attached onboarding document.</p>",
        "attachments": [
            {
                "fileName": "onboarding.txt",
                "mediaType": "text/plain",
                "file": "SGVsbG8sIFdlbGNvbWUgdG8gQ29sbGFiU3BoZXJlIQ==",
                "fileSize": 32
            }
        ]
    }
}
